                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "results were obtained in the first year of the HALy.ID project, we do not discuss them here. Instead, we focus on the computer vision algorithms used to detect BMSB in images collected autonomously by the drone. From this perspective, it is evident that the majority of achievements related to BMSB detection have been generated within the HALy.ID project. Furthermore, unlike others, we are currently exploring solutions that can accurately determine the BMSB's position directly from aerial or in- field images."
                                }
