                                        1269,
                                        897,
                                        2319,
                                        2032
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " for training, validation, and test sets, respectively, by automatically and randomly distributing the indexed dataset with a script created for this purpose. The dataset contains 402 images and, as a consequence of the slicing technique, is decomposed in 17 766 patches of which 423 are positive ones (with BMSB)."
                                }
